CHANGES 
-----------------------
* 2025-04-17
  RbowtieCuda Version: 1.0.1

  - The package is available on Bioconductor

* 2025-08-23
  RbowtieCuda Version: 1.0.8

  - nvBowtie, nvBWT and nvbio_test propagate their error messages to the R interface
  - Improved diagnostic messages during package installation
  - Improved program stability
  - Faster startup
  - Compatible with CUDA 13.0
  - The program needs 16 GB of RAM to be compiled (with Sys.setenv(MAKEFLAGS="-j8"))


